      <title>随着集会力量的消退，特朗普向棕榈滩亿万富翁示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-courts-palm-beach-billionaires-as-power-of-his-rallies-fades</link>
