    <item>
      <title>特鲁多承诺再提供数十亿美元的公寓建设贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，即将出台的联邦预算将在公寓建设贷款计划中再投入 150 亿加元（合 111 亿美元），这是他为解决加拿大人口激增导致的住房短缺问题所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
